{"tid":34722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[用腦]藍綠悖論","createTime":"2016-12-11T15:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T16:09:49.000Z","uid":61095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11bf06fbf983f7595cf594cb6a8afa0c16f2866d","tid":34722,"uid":61095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:52:46.000Z","msg":"假設：有一個人，他有一種奇怪的色盲症。他看到的兩種顏色和別人不一樣，他把藍色看成綠色，把綠色看成藍色。<br />\n<br />\n但是他自己並不知道他跟別人不一樣，別人看到的天空是藍色的，他看到的是綠色的，但是他和別人的叫法都一樣，都是「藍色」；小草是綠色的，他看到的卻是藍色的，但是他把藍色叫做「綠色」。所以，他自己和別人都不知道他和別人的不同。<br />\n<br />\n問：怎麼讓他知道自己和別人不一樣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/tech/gq38n8.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Ftech%2Fgq38n8.html&d=QysPipF0KpTl4tUHcs7bb3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=0713b0b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/tech/gq38n8.html</a>"},{"pid":"305efa998e0986793e6a1cb98b959a068387d61d","tid":34722,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:53:11.000Z","msg":"我以前都諗過呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030a74e2aadd982c8857dfa395388474938fb723","tid":34722,"uid":61095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:56:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以前都諗過呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇懷疑過自己"},{"pid":"1896ce1e9e4b3289bc5eda8c3db9d9f6e86931f0","tid":34722,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:56:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我以前都諗過呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇懷疑過自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce5ed357239cf8a0fe6686e7e0394f9ca2dbf4c","tid":34722,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:57:17.000Z","msg":"思考過類似問題"},{"pid":"f51b4d62c5347f583d0c71f91afb22bbef2a9927","tid":34722,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:57:57.000Z","msg":"無辦法"},{"pid":"304eab3fbc45024196e3008246a3ad6585acba7c","tid":34722,"uid":38684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"我記得<br />\n對視覺，顏色即理解係認知番黎<br />\n即係後天既<br />\n所以<br />\n嚴格黎講佢冇色盲<br />\n因為佢的確係理解到<br />\n正常人既藍為藍，綠為綠<br />\n亦分辨同其中既不同<br />\n所以無法判斷<br />\n因為其實佢冇色盲"}]}